data.description: Assumable FHA loan at 7.25%!!!! Welcome to 902 Savannah St, a stunning one-year-old home located in the charming town of Cowpens, SC. This exceptional property offers a spacious open floor plan, a large yead, and the added benefit of no HOA fees. Step inside and be greeted by the bright and airy living spaces, thoughtfully designed to maximize comfort and functionality. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with loved ones. The heart of the home is the impressive kitchen, featuring a generous island that serves as a focal point and provides ample space for meal preparation and casual dining. With its modern appliances, abundant storage, and stylish finishes, this kitchen is a dream come true for any culinary enthusiast. The master suite is a true retreat, offering a peaceful sanctuary to unwind after a long day. The on-suite bathroom boasts contemporary fixtures, creating a luxurious experience. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide comfort and privacy for family or quests. Outside discover a spacious yard, offering endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening or simply enjoying the fresh air. The absence of HOA fees provides the freedom to personalize and utilize the space as desired. Situated in the desirable town of Cowpens, this home offers a peaceful and welcoming community with convenient access to local amenities, including shops, restaurants, and park. Experience the best of small town living at 902 Savannah St. Don't miss this opportunity to own this exceptional home! Schedule a showing today and discover the beauty and convenience of 902 Savannah St yourself.
